---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
export const prerender = false;
---

<PageLayout
  title="About UKF Services | Dubai Freight Forwarder Since 2008"
  description="Founded in 2008, UKF Services is Dubai's trusted freight forwarder operating from Dubai Cargo Village. 200+ UAE exporters served, 100% customs compliance record."
>

  <!-- PAGE HERO -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container about-hero-content">
      <p class="about-eyebrow">Our Story</p>
      <h1 class="about-title">Built in Dubai.<br/>Trusted Across the Globe.</h1>
      <p class="about-subtitle">Since 2008, UKF Services has operated from the heart of Dubai Cargo Village — building one of the UAE's most trusted specialist freight operations, one shipment at a time.</p>
      <div class="about-hero-stats">
        <div class="about-stat">
          <strong>2008</strong>
          <span>Year founded</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="about-stat">
          <strong>17+</strong>
          <span>Years at DCV</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="about-stat">
          <strong>200+</strong>
          <span>UAE exporters served</span>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="about-stat">
          <strong>100%</strong>
          <span>Customs compliance</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OUR STORY -->
  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="container story-grid">
      <div class="story-timeline fade-up">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2008</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Founded at Dubai Cargo Village</h3>
            <p>UKF Sea & Air Cargo Services LLC established at Office 2056-A, Entrance 4, Dubai Cargo Village. From day one, positioned as a specialist forwarder — not a generalist, not a broker.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2010</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>UAE Customs Expertise Established</h3>
            <p>Built direct relationships with UAE Customs Authority and Dubai Airport Freezone. Began handling complex regulated cargo — pharmaceuticals, electronics, precious metals.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2015</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>100+ Client Milestone</h3>
            <p>Surpassed 100 active UAE exporter clients. Expanded service offering to include full project cargo handling and temperature-controlled logistics.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2019</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Indonesia Corridor Launch</h3>
            <p>Developed dedicated UAE–Indonesia trade lane expertise covering Tanjung Priok, Batam, and Surabaya. First GCC forwarder to specialise in halal cargo documentation for this corridor.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-year">2024</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>200+ Exporters. Zero Customs Penalties.</h3>
            <p>Crossed 200 UAE exporters served milestone. Maintained a 100% UAE customs compliance record across 17 years — not a single penalty across thousands of shipments.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item timeline-item--current">
          <div class="timeline-year">Now</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Dubai's Specialist Freight Partner</h3>
            <p>Operating from the same Dubai Cargo Village location. Same commitment. Same standards. Serving UAE trading companies who cannot afford logistics surprises.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="story-content fade-up">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">Why We Exist</p>
        <h2 class="story-heading">The Antidote to Logistics Drama.</h2>
        <p class="story-body">Most freight forwarders are generalists. They handle everything from everywhere to everywhere — which means they are specialists in nothing. When complexity arises, they escalate. When regulations tighten, they guess. When cargo goes wrong, they disappear.</p>
        <p class="story-body">UKF was built on the opposite model. We chose Dubai Cargo Village and we stayed. We chose specific corridors and mastered them. We chose UAE customs expertise and built a compliance record that has never been broken.</p>
        <p class="story-body">Our clients are CFOs, supply chain directors and VP Logistics at UAE trading companies. They chose us because they cannot afford surprises — and we have never given them one.</p>

        <div class="story-values">
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">🎯</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Specialist, not generalist</h4>
              <p>We operate specific corridors and know them better than anyone. UAE to UK. UAE to Europe. UAE–Indonesia. That depth of knowledge is what protects your cargo.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">🤝</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Relationships, not transactions</h4>
              <p>10+ clients have been with us for over a decade. We don't win on price — we win on trust, reliability, and the fact that we pick up the phone.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="value-item">
            <div class="value-icon">📋</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Compliance without compromise</h4>
              <p>100% UAE customs compliance record since 2008. We don't take shortcuts. Every document, every declaration, every HS code — verified before submission.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CEO SECTION -->
  <section class="ceo-section fade-up">
    <div class="container ceo-grid">
      <div class="ceo-card">
        <div class="ceo-avatar">MS</div>
        <div class="ceo-badge">CEO & Founder</div>
        <h2 class="ceo-name">Mirza Salim Baig</h2>
        <p class="ceo-title">Chief Executive Officer<br/>UKF Sea & Air Cargo Services LLC</p>
        <div class="ceo-credentials">
          <span>25+ years in international freight</span>
          <span>Dubai Cargo Village since 2008</span>
          <span>UAE Customs specialist</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ceo-content">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">Leadership</p>
        <h2 class="ceo-heading">The Person Behind Every Shipment.</h2>
        <p class="ceo-body">Mirza Salim Baig has spent over 25 years in international freight and logistics — and the last 17 of those building UKF Services from Dubai Cargo Village into one of the UAE's most trusted specialist freight operations.</p>
        <p class="ceo-body">His philosophy is straightforward: freight is a trust business. When a client hands you a $22 million gold shipment, or a temperature-sensitive pharmaceutical consignment, or a complex multi-leg project cargo movement — they are trusting you with their business, their reputation, and sometimes their compliance record.</p>
        <p class="ceo-body">"Our job is to make your supply chain invisible. You should never have to worry about it. If you are worrying about logistics, something has already gone wrong."</p>
        <blockquote class="ceo-quote">
          "17 years at Dubai Cargo Village has given us something no new entrant can buy — institutional knowledge. We know the customs officers. We know the airline cargo managers. We know which documentation gets flagged and why. That knowledge protects our clients every single day."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="ceo-signature">— Mirza Salim Baig, CEO</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LOCATION -->
  <section class="location-section fade-up">
    <div class="container location-grid">
      <div class="location-content">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">Where We Operate</p>
        <h2 class="location-heading">Dubai Cargo Village.<br/>The Centre of UAE Trade.</h2>
        <p class="location-body">Dubai Cargo Village is one of the world's busiest air cargo facilities — handling over 800,000 tonnes of freight annually, operating 24/7, adjacent to Dubai International Airport's dedicated cargo terminals.</p>
        <p class="location-body">We have operated from the same location since 2008. Not a virtual office. Not a registered address. This is where our team works every day — inside the system, next to the runways, with the relationships that move cargo when others cannot.</p>
        <div class="location-detail">
          <div class="location-item">
            <span class="location-label">Address</span>
            <span class="location-value">Office No. 2056-A, First Floor, Entrance No. 4, Dubai Cargo Village, Dubai, UAE</span>
          </div>
          <div class="location-item">
            <span class="location-label">Phone</span>
            <span class="location-value"><a href="tel:+971552572837">+971 55 257 2837</a></span>
          </div>
          <div class="location-item">
            <span class="location-label">Email</span>
            <span class="location-value"><a href="mailto:info@ukfservices.com">info@ukfservices.com</a></span>
          </div>
          <div class="location-item">
            <span class="location-label">Hours</span>
            <span class="location-value">Sunday–Thursday: 08:00–18:00 GST</span>
          </div>
          <div class="location-item">
            <span class="location-label">WhatsApp</span>
            <span class="location-value"><a href="https://wa.me/971552572837" target="_blank" rel="noopener">+971 55 257 2837</a></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="location-visual">
        <div class="location-card">
          <div class="location-card-header">
            <span class="location-card-badge">📍 Live Location</span>
          </div>
          <div class="location-card-map">
            <div class="map-placeholder">
              <span class="map-icon">✈</span>
              <p>Dubai Cargo Village</p>
              <p class="map-sub">Adjacent to Dubai International Airport</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="location-card-facts">
            <div class="location-fact">
              <strong>800,000+</strong>
              <span>Tonnes handled annually at DCV</span>
            </div>
            <div class="location-fact">
              <strong>24/7</strong>
              <span>Operational — we're always accessible</span>
            </div>
            <div class="location-fact">
              <strong>17 years</strong>
              <span>Same location, same team, same standards</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BOTTOM CTA -->
  <section class="about-cta-section fade-up">
    <div class="container about-cta-inner">
      <div>
        <h2>Ready to work with us?</h2>
        <p>Same-day response. Itemised quote. No obligation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-cta-btns">
        <a href="/contact" class="about-cta-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/971552572837" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="about-cta-wa">WhatsApp Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- JSON-LD -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">{JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "AboutPage",
    "name": "About UKF Services",
    "description": "UKF Sea & Air Cargo Services LLC — Dubai's specialist freight forwarder since 2008.",
    "mainEntity": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "UKF Services",
      "legalName": "UKF Sea & Air Cargo Services LLC",
      "foundingDate": "2008",
      "slogan": "The Antidote to Logistics Drama",
      "address": {
        "@type": "PostalAddress",
        "streetAddress": "Office No. 2056-A, First Floor, Entrance No. 4, Dubai Cargo Village",
        "addressLocality": "Dubai",
        "addressCountry": "AE"
      }
    }
  })}</script>

</PageLayout>

<style>
  .section-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: block;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .about-hero {
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, #0f2a50 60%, var(--navy-mid) 100%);
    padding: 120px 0 80px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .about-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    right: -20%;
    width: 600px;
    height: 600px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201,168,76,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .about-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: url('/images/hero-cargo.webp') center/cover no-repeat;
    opacity: 0.08;
  }
  .about-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .about-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: block;
  }
  .about-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 58px);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .about-subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(15px, 2vw, 18px);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .about-hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
    padding-top: 40px;
  }
  .about-stat {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0 40px;
  }
  .about-stat strong {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .about-stat span {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .about-stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 48px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .about-stat-divider { display: none; }
    .about-stat { padding: 12px 20px; }
  }

  /* STORY */
  .story-section { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--white); }
  .story-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .story-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  /* Timeline */
  .story-timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 32px; }
  .story-timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 8px;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gold), rgba(201,168,76,0.1));
  }
  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .timeline-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -38px;
    top: 8px;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gold);
    border: 3px solid var(--white);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--gold);
  }
  .timeline-item--current::before {
    background: var(--navy);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--gold);
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    left: -40px;
    top: 6px;
  }
  .timeline-year {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .timeline-content h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .timeline-content p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.7; }

  /* Story content */
  .story-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(26px, 3vw, 36px);
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .story-body { font-size: 15px; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .story-values { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; margin-top: 36px; }
  .value-item { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .value-icon { font-size: 24px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
  .value-item h4 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .value-item p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.65; margin: 0; }

  /* CEO */
  .ceo-section {
    background: var(--off-white);
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
  }
  .ceo-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 320px 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .ceo-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .ceo-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--navy-mid) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.25);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 36px;
    text-align: center;
    position: sticky;
    top: 100px;
  }
  .ceo-avatar {
    width: 80px; height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), var(--gold-light));
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
  }
  .ceo-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .ceo-name {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 24px;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .ceo-title { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .ceo-credentials {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    padding-top: 20px;
  }
  .ceo-credentials span {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    padding: 6px 12px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .ceo-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 34px);
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .ceo-body { font-size: 15px; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .ceo-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 17px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--navy);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.06);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    margin: 28px 0 12px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .ceo-signature { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-400); font-style: italic; }

  /* LOCATION */
  .location-section { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--white); }
  .location-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .location-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .location-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 34px);
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .location-body { font-size: 15px; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .location-detail { margin-top: 32px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  .location-item { display: flex; gap: 16px; }
  .location-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    min-width: 72px;
    padding-top: 1px;
  }
  .location-value { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.5; }
  .location-value a { color: var(--navy); transition: color 0.2s; }
  .location-value a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

  .location-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, var(--navy-mid) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .location-card-header {
    padding: 16px 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  .location-card-badge {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold);
  }
  .location-card-map {
    height: 200px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  .map-placeholder { text-align: center; }
  .map-icon { font-size: 40px; display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .map-placeholder p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0; }
  .map-sub { font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top: 4px !important; }
  .location-card-facts {
    padding: 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .location-fact { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: center; }
  .location-fact strong {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--gold);
    min-width: 80px;
  }
  .location-fact span { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); }

  /* ABOUT CTA */
  .about-cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, #0f2a50 100%);
    padding: 64px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
  }
  .about-cta-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 32px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .about-cta-inner h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px);
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .about-cta-inner p { font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
  .about-cta-btns { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .about-cta-primary {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--navy);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 13px 28px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .about-cta-primary:hover { background: var(--gold-light); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .about-cta-wa {
    background: #25D366;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 13px 28px;
    border-radius: 6px;
